card.text:
When Spectral Sabers enters, create a 1/1 white Spirit creature token with flying and attach this Equipment to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 for each artifact you control.
Equip {3}

Equipped creature gets +1/+1.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, create a 1/1 blue Drake creature token with flying that's tapped and attacking. Exile that token at the beginning of the next end step.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature has flying.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, you may exile target nonland card from your graveyard with mana value less than its power. If you do, you may cast a copy of that card without paying its mana cost. (A copy of a permanent spell becomes a token.)
Equip {3}

Equipped creature gets +2/+2 and has protection from multicolored.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, exile the top card of that player's library. Until end of turn, you may play that card. Then plunder. (Create a Treasure token, or sacrifice an artifact to draw a card.)
Equip {2}

When Corsair Firebomb enters, it deals 2 damage to up to one target creature or planeswalker.
Whenever equipped creature becomes blocked, it deals 1 damage to each creature blocking it.
Equip {1}
